OL,3,CDog walkers face #1,000 fine if they
OL,4,Cbreach new restrictions in Hastings
OL,6,FDog owners in Hastings will no longer
OL,7,Fbe allowed to walk their pets on parts
OL,8,Fof the beach during the summer.
OL,10,FHastings Borough Council has brought
OL,11,Fin new guidelines for pet owners who
OL,12,Fface a #1,000 fine if they are not
OL,13,Ffollowed.
OL,15,FUnder the new rules, no more than six
OL,16,Fdogs can be be taken out by one person
OL,17,Fand pets must be kept on a lead along
OL,18,Fthe promenade.
