OL,6,FDogs are also not allowed in
OL,7,Fchildren's play areas, multi-use games
OL,8,Fareas, skate parks, tennis courts or
OL,9,Fbowls greens.
OL,11,FThe council says anyone who breaches
OL,12,Fthe new restrictions could be given an
OL,13,Fon the spot fine of up to #100, or
OL,14,Fprosecuted in court with a fine of up
OL,15,Fto #1000.
